PhoneGap implementation for Samsung Bada.

Support for: Acceleration, Geolocation (native and browser), Network, Device

Missing support: Camera, Contacts (Wip), Compass (Wip), File, Notifications

Steps to build a PhoneGap app
* Download Source Code
* Import in bada C++ IDE
* Put your HTML/CSS files in the Res/ folder
* Build&Run!

Happy Coding!
